    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">If inclement weather hits, whether you’re camping, responding to an emergency situation, boating or preparing a survival kit. the ASR Outdoor Waterproof Paper Pocket Spiral Notebook Travel Journal Field Notes Notepad is ready to weather the elements with you. Measuring 3 x 5 inches, the notepad includes 50 white, lined pages, a waterproof cover, top bound secure spiral, side ruler for measuring inches or millimeters and comes with a three-inch pencil. Whether you’re planning a backpacking adventure, need a notepad to jot down field notes or just want to have some scrap paper on hand for your next camping trip, the ASR Outdoor notepad is lightweight, pocket-sized and compact, making it incredibly portable and great for all kinds of travel</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Waterproof Paper Pocket Travel Spiral Notebook Field Notepad Journal</h2>\n  <p>If inclement weather hits, whether you’re camping, responding to an emergency situation, boating or preparing a survival kit. the ASR Outdoor Waterproof Paper Pocket Spiral Notebook Travel Journal Field Notes Notepad is ready to weather the elements with you.</p>\n  <p>Measuring 3 x 5 inches, the notepad includes 50 white, lined pages, a waterproof cover, top bound secure spiral, side ruler for measuring inches or millimeters and comes with a three-inch pencil.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>WATERPROOF &amp; WEATHERPROOF NOTEBOOK:</strong> Measuring 3 x 5 inches, the notepad includes 50 white lined pages, a waterproof cover, top bound secure spiral, green ruler for measuring inches or millimeters and a 3 inch pencil</li>\n    <li><strong>PERFECT TRAVEL JOURNAL:</strong> ASR Outdoor notepad is lightweight, pocket-sized and compact, making it incredibly portable and great for all kinds of travel</li>\n    <li><strong>WATERPROOF NOTEPAD COVER:</strong> A tough but flexible notepad cover in green colorway will repel water, moisture and other liquids, keeping your writing paper with notes safe and dry</li>\n    <li><strong>MULTI-DISCIPLINARY NOTEPAD:</strong> This notepad is not limited to just camping, outdoor excursions or survival kits; it’s also ideal for journalists, lab workers, emergency first responders, tactical professionals or police or law enforcement officers.</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Product Dimension: 3 x 5 x 0.5 inches; Color: Green; Lined Pages: 50; Page Color: White; 3-inch Pencil Included</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/camping_hiking/OD-NB35WP_waterproof_notepad_detail_01.jpg\" alt=\"If inclement weather hits, whether you’re camping, responding to an emergency situation, boating or preparing a survival kit\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASROWPNB</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058484512</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Green</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Whether you’re planning a backpacking adventure, need a notepad to jot down field notes or just want to have some scrap paper on hand for your next camping trip, the ASR Outdoor notepad is lightweight, pocket-sized and compact, making it incredibly portable and great for all kinds of travel.</p>\n  <p>Lastly, this notepad is not limited to just camping, outdoor excursions or survival kits; it’s also ideal for journalists, lab workers, emergency first responders, tactical professionals or police or law enforcement officers, where work events or situations can outdoors in less than desirable weather conditions.</p>\n  <p>This memo pad is ready to accompany you on adventure you set out for, perfect for any outdoor situation where notetaking, fact recording or capturing creativity or new ideas are needed.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
